King's Highway, at the S.W. corner of Farragut Road, showing the
Johannes Ditmars farmhouse. Van Wyck in his book titled Keskachauge
states - - - - - ''stands probably near site of Jan Stevense (Voorhees)
house - - - - -- mentioned in 1695-1696''. The Ditmars were lineal
descendants of Jan Stevense (Voorhees).

and Mam hattan Beach R.E.
